````

### 设置IP
`sudo vim /etc/network/interfaces`

```
# 动态IP
iface eth0 inet dhcp

# 静态IP
iface eth0 inet static
address 10.0.1.145
netmask 255.255.255.0
gateway 10.0.1.1
```

设置DNS: `vi /etc/resolv.conf`

```
nameserver 8.8.8.8
```

设置后保存，重启：`sudo /etc/init.d/networking restart`

