## 备份树莓派镜像

````
sudo dd bs=4m if=/dev/rdisk1 of=rpi_hashratio_20140425.img
tar zcvf rpi_hashratio_20140425.img.tar.gz ./rpi_hashratio_20140425.img

# img文件与SD一样大小，这里是8G，压缩文件大约900MB
````